FFT periods

Source: R/fft_base.R
fft_period.Rd

Fast Fourier Transform (FFT): periods for a real signal of length t (in time) with n samples.

Usage

fft_period(f)

Arguments

f

num. The harmonics frequencies.

Value

\(p\) the harmonics periods.

Examples


fft_freq(201, 10) %>%
  fft_period()
